name: Fragments through Life
description: In this work, I wondered how there are opposite curtains acting on the same being in different ways. And how each lived experience shapes a person, sometimes even shared in different contexts. I believe that duality exists as a reminder to put what is important to us in perspective. Priorities, tastes, pleasures and dislikes. The victories and the failures; And that only happens when you live. It lives side by side.
